Is there a way to pass a custom prompt to the composable graph. The query method take query config object but not able to figure out a way to pass in custom prompt ? 
The following statement failed.
res = indx.query(query_str,**text_qa_template= my_prompt**);

The current version can easily and succesfully *query* existing Pinecone namespaces but can't create new ones or delete them. With this change, you can use the same syntax as your query:
```py

insert_kwargs = {
    "pinecone_kwargs": {
        "namespace": namespace,
    }
}

index.insert(document=(Document(text, doc_id=doc_id)), **insert_kwargs)
```

And it will handle your custom namespace:
